title: Ostendorf and Wilson Crowned Viking Days King and Queen (Augustana College)
text: ( Source : Augustana College ) October 12 , 2015 Seniors Tori Wilson and Brad Ostendorf were crowned Viking Days Queen and King at Coronation on Monday. Wilson, a senior from Wayzata, Minnesota , is a Spanish and K-12 education double major.
